Insider Activity


Individual




April Miller Boise



Ms. April M. Boise is Secretary, Senior Vice President & General Counsel at Meritor, Inc. and a Principal at Thompson Hine LLP. She is on the Board of Directors at The Cleveland Museum of Art. Ms. Boise was previously employed as Secretary, Senior Vice President & General Counsel by AVINTIV, Inc. She received her undergraduate degree from Stephen M. Ross School of Business and a graduate degree from The University of Chicago Law School.



